  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Assessment of recent trends of deforestation and forest degradation and related drivers using SEPAL (CAFI)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is global in nature. As part of the project&apos;s approach, FAO proposes to develop a global, standard, large-scale methodology to assess forest dynamics, using cloud-computing solutions and open-source tools to map disturbances and quantify direct drivers of deforestation and forest degradation. The methodology will be tested to assess deforestation and forest degradation trends and their associated current and historical direct drivers in six Central Africa countries.</narrative>
  </description>
